Definition: the process of using your mind to consider something carefully
Example: thinking always made him frown; she paused for thought
Synonyms: verb, cognition, think, thought, thought_process, cerebration, cerebrate, intellection, mentation, higher_cognitive_process, the, process, of, using, your, mind, to, consider, something, carefully, always, made, him, frown, she, paused, for
Category: noun.cognition
